'''美國商會'''（'''{{lang|en|United States Chamber of Commerce}}'''，簡稱：'''{{lang|en|USCC}}'''）是一個代表多間[[企業|企業]]和[[協會|貿易協會]]的[[美國|美國]][[倡导团体|遊說團體]]，並不是[[美國政府|美國政府]]的官方單位。

美國商會由多位政策專家、遊說家和律師組成。在[[政治|政治]]方面，美國商會一般被認為屬於[[保守主義|保守主義]]團體。美國商會通常支持[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]候選人，但有時也會支持保守派的[[民主黨_(美國)|民主黨]]候選人<ref>{{cite news | url=http://articles.latimes.com/2010/oct/08/news/la-pn-chamber-ads-20101009 | work=Los Angeles Times | first1=Matea | last1=Gold | first2=Kim | last2=Geiger | title=Republican-leaning U.S. Chamber of Commerce buys ads supporting Democrats | date=2010-10-08 | accessdate=2014-02-27 | archive-date=2010-10-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101013183354/http://articles.latimes.com/2010/oct/08/news/la-pn-chamber-ads-20101009 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Verini">{{cite web |last=Verini |first=James |url=http://www.washingtonmonthly.com/features/2010/1007.verini.html |title=Show Him the Money by James Verini |publisher=Washington Monthly |date=1912-04-12 |accessdate=2010-11-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101230175601/http://www.washingtonmonthly.com/features/2010/1007.verini.html |archivedate=2010-12-30 }}</ref>。美國商會是美國最大的遊說團體之一，每年的開銷金額超越了其他遊說團體<ref name="toplobby">{{cite web | title = Top lobbyists in the US | url = http://www.opensecrets.org/lobby/top.php | accessdate = 2009-07-08 | archive-date = 2012-04-15 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/66wuJh3yT?url=http://www.opensecrets.org/lobby/top.php | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.politico.com/news/stories/1009/28471.html|title=U.S. Chamber: $34.7 million in lobbying|first=Jonathan|last=Allen|publisher=Politico|date=2009-10-20|access-date=2014-02-27|archive-date=2012-04-15|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66wuKFuzd?url=http://www.politico.com/news/stories/1009/28471.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 立場 ==
=== 立法相關 ===
* 美國商會反對美國政府使用[[美國政府停擺|關閉聯邦政府]]和[[國債|國債]]上限作為談判籌碼。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.uschamber.com/issues/letters/2013/multi-industry-coalition-letter-regarding-continuing-resolution-and-debt-limit |title=存档副本 |access-date=2014-02-27 |archive-date=2013-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131207023731/http://www.uschamber.com/issues/letters/2013/multi-industry-coalition-letter-regarding-continuing-resolution-and-debt-limit |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* 美國商會支持《[[禁止网络盗版法案|禁止网络盗版法案]]》（SOPA）。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.readwriteweb.com/enterprise/2011/11/cautious-optimism-follows-sopa.php |title=Cautious Optimism Follows SOPA (2011) |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111122221907/http://www.readwriteweb.com/enterprise/2011/11/cautious-optimism-follows-sopa.php |archivedate=2011-11-22 }}</ref>
* 美國商會支持企業[[全球化|全球化]]、[[自由貿易|自由貿易]]和[[外判|外包]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ventureoutsource.com/contract-manufacturing/executive-interviews/2007/tom-donohue-u-s-chamber-of-commerce-on-outsourcing-and-offshoring |title=Tom Donohue, U.S. Chamber of Commerce on outsourcing and offshoring (2007) Interview conducted and hosted by |publisher=Ventureoutsource.com |date= |accessdate=2010-11-05 |archive-date=2021-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211233246/https://www.ventureoutsource.com/contract-manufacturing/executive-interviews/2007/tom-donohue-u-s-chamber-of-commerce-on-outsourcing-and-offshoring |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* 對於金融管制的反對立場：<ref name="Verini"/>
** 美國商會認為部分改革是必要的，但反對已通過的《{{link-en|杜德-法蘭克華爾街改革與消費者保護法|Dodd–Frank Wall Street Reform and Consumer Protection Act}}》。商會指出，該法案將造成[[貸款|貸款]]困難。<ref name="Verini"/>
** 美國商會進行遊說活動反對《[[沙賓法案|沙賓法案]]》。<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.businessweek.com/magazine/content/05_03/b3916031_mz011.htm| work=Business Week| first=David| last=Henry| date=2005-01-17| title=Death, Taxes, & Sarbanes-Oxley?| accessdate=2014-02-27| archive-date=2010-08-30| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100830043635/http://www.businessweek.com/magazine/content/05_03/b3916031_mz011.htm| dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 美國商會反對《{{link-en|DISCLOSE法案|DISCLOSE Act}}》，該法案目標是為了限制其他國家對美國選舉的影響。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-503544_162-20011683-503544.html | work=CBS News | first=Brian | last=Montopoli | title=Obama Slams GOP For Opposing DISCLOSE Act Meant to Expose "Shadow Groups" Behind Ads | date=2010-07-26 | accessdate=2014-02-27 | archive-date=2013-05-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511225116/http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-503544_162-20011683-503544.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>
* 美國商會反對《{{link-en|國民平價醫療法案|Affordable Health Care for America Act}}》<ref name="Verini"/>，雖然商會認為美國醫療保險制度需要改革，但認為應尋求以[[市場機制|市場機制]]為基礎的解決方式。
* 美國商會反對針對[[全球暖化|氣候變遷]]所採取的行動。商會認為氣候變遷是事實，但不認同暖化是由人類行為造成的科學結論，並質疑有任何方法能有效減緩氣候變遷現象。商會強調，針對氣候變遷採取的解決政策可能影響經濟。<ref name="latimes_climate">{{cite news|last=Tankersley|first=Jim|title=U.S. Chamber of Commerce seeks trial on global warming|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2009/aug/25/nation/na-climate-trial25|accessdate=2010-12-13|newspaper=The Los Angeles Times|date=2009-08-25|archive-date=2012-04-15|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66wuMUUXi?url=http://articles.latimes.com/2009/aug/25/nation/na-climate-trial25|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="reuters_climate">{{cite news|last=Gardner|first=Timothy|title=Apple, citing climate, tells U.S. Chamber iQuit|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSN0519277320091005|accessdate=2010-12-13|newspaper=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|date=2009-10-05|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204045659/https://www.reuters.com/article/idUSN0519277320091005|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 美國商會支持《[[2009年美國復蘇與再投資法案|2009年美國復蘇與再投資法案]]》。<ref name="Verini"/>
* 美國商會支持《{{link-en|2013年聯邦通信委員會合併報告法案|Federal Communications Commission Consolidated Reporting Act of 2013}}》。<ref name=uschambcommer1>{{cite web|title=Letter Supporting the "FCC Process Reform Act of 2013" and the "FCC Consolidated Reporting Act of 2013"|url=http://www.uschamber.com/issues/letters/2013/letter-supporting-%E2%80%9Cfcc-process-reform-act-2013%E2%80%9D-and-%E2%80%9Cfcc-consolidated-reporting-|publisher=U.S. Chamber of Commerce|accessdate=2013-09-12|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130906222127/http://www.uschamber.com/issues/letters/2013/letter-supporting-%E2%80%9Cfcc-process-reform-act-2013%E2%80%9D-and-%E2%80%9Cfcc-consolidated-reporting-|archivedate=2013-09-06}}</ref>
* 美國商會支持《{{link-en|2013年減少過度期限責任法案|Reducing Excessive Deadline Obligations Act of 2013}}》。<ref name=chamcom1>{{cite web|last=Josten|first=R. Bruce|title=Letter to the U.S. House of Representatives Supporting H.R. 2279, H.R. 2318, and H.R. 2226 (CERCLA and RCRA)|url=http://www.uschamber.com/issues/letters/2013/letter-us-house-representatives-supporting-hr-2279-hr-2318-and-hr-2226-cercla-an|publisher=U.S. Chamber of Commerce|accessdate=2014-01-07|date=2013-07-30|archive-date=2014-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140107195048/http://www.uschamber.com/issues/letters/2013/letter-us-house-representatives-supporting-hr-2279-hr-2318-and-hr-2226-cercla-an|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 法院案件 ===
* 美國商會反對[[亞利桑那州|亞利桑那州]]強制僱主需檢查雇員的移民身份狀態，包括在[[美國最高法院|美國最高法院]]中公開抗辯反對。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2011/US/05/26/scotus.arizona.law/index.html?hpt=T2|title=Supreme Court backs Arizona immigration law that punishes businesses|last=Mears|first=Bill|date=26 May 2011|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|accessdate=26 May 2011|archive-date=2017-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170620022707/http://www.cnn.com/2011/US/05/26/scotus.arizona.law/index.html?hpt=T2|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 在[[联合公民诉联邦选举委员会案|联合公民诉联邦选举委员会案]]中，美國商會以[[法院之友|法院之友]]的方式向美國最高法院表達支持公司[[法人|法人化]]，以讓企業資助候選人的政治獻金可不受管制。部分代表[[中小企業|中小企業]]的遊說團體，對此與美國商會持相反立場。<ref name="amiba">[http://www.amiba.net/resources/news-archive/release-reaction-cu-fec-ruling Independent Business Advocates Condemn U.S. Supreme Court's Decision in Citizens United] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921053904/http://www.amiba.net/resources/news-archive/release-reaction-cu-fec-ruling |date=2013-09-21 }}.</ref>

